  "text": "MRI scans were performed on a 1 T Siemens Magnetom Impact (Siemens Healthcare, Frimley, UK). Staging scans were carried out as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Dynamic scans used a sagittal 2D T 1 -weighted FLASH sequence (TR/TE ¼ 130/6.5 ms, FOV ¼ 290 Â 290 Â 5 mm, matrix ¼ 256 Â 256, NSA ¼ 1, a ¼ 701) with a temporal resolution of 25 s. One sequence of nine contiguous slices covering the whole-tumour volume was obtained before and seven after injection of 0.1 mmol kg À1 body weight Gd-DTPA.",
